genresAdvancedInfo.name: slovak electronic
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Slovak electronic is a genre of music that combines electronic beats with traditional Slovakian folk melodies. It is characterized by its use of synthesizers and drum machines, as well as its incorporation of traditional instruments like the fujara and the koncovka. The result is a unique sound that blends the old and the new, creating a fresh and exciting musical experience.
